show.description: One day, William, who's living an innocent life, finds out a shocking truth that turns his world upside down. He discovers that Kevin, the son he's raising with so much love, is not his biological child. Before he can even process this, another heartbreaking truth comes out — his wife has been cheating on him for many years. In this tragic moment, William realizes his true hidden nature. He's not just an ordinary man... he's a God of War. What will William do now? What dangers await him at this moment of realizing his divinity? Is William about to unleash a war that will tear the world apart?
